1. *Meksiko* je velika zemlja. (Mexico is a large country.)
2. Želela bih da posetim *Meksiko*. (I would like to visit Mexico.)
3. *Meksiko* se nalazi u Severnoj Americi. (Mexico is located in North America.)
4. Moj omiljeni meksički restoran služi ukusnu hranu. (*Meksiko* - referring to Mexican cuisine - My favorite Mexican restaurant serves delicious food.)
5. Danas učimo o istoriji *Meksika*. (Today we are learning about the history of Mexico.)
6. Ovaj duks je kupljen u *Meksiku*. (This sweatshirt was bought in Mexico.)
7. *Meksiko* je poznat po svojoj muzici i plesu. (Mexico is known for its music and dance.)
8. Meksikanac koji živi u mom komšiluku je vrlo prijatan. (The Mexican who lives in my neighborhood is very pleasant.)
9. Nacionalna valuta *Meksika* je pezo. (The national currency of Mexico is the peso.)
10. *Meksiko* ima bogatu kulturu. (Mexico has a rich culture.)

(Note: The star symbol (*) is used to highlight the word "Meksiko" in each sentence.)